<chapter title="Mingle Plus" id="mingle_plus">
  <section title="What is Mingle Plus?">
    <p>Since <cref topic="whats_new_in_release_12_2">release 12.2</cref>, Mingle has been available in two editions: <strong>Mingle</strong> and <strong>Mingle Plus</strong>. The main feature set that differentiates Mingle and Mingle Plus is the <cref topic="program"><strong>Program</strong></cref>. To use Mingle's Plus features, you will need a valid Mingle Plus license.</p>
    <p>Please visit our website to understand how to <exref url="http://support.thoughtworks.com/entries/21784662-mingle-plus-faq">get a Mingle Plus license</exref>.</p>
